data.description: Spacious, 5 bedroom 3 bathroom house nestled in a quiet subdivision. Hawkins Preserve located right near providing miles of hiking and biking. This house has so much to offer including 2 master suits and all of the exquisite updates that have been done. Beautiful hardwood floor throughout. The kitchen has been newly remodeled with an astonishing farm house sink. Mature landscaping front and back with automatic sprinklers. The back yard is simply an oasis, set up for entertaining or just simply relaxation. This property has been very well maintained and loved with over 2300 square foot you will never feel the need for more space. Conveniently only an hour away from many of Colorado's major attractions. Schedule your showing today this home will not last!
